2011-09-21T20:38:38Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-21/galleon-co-founder-rajaratnam-s-sentencing-delayed-to-oct-13.html
Galleon Group LLC co-founder Raj
Rajaratnam’s sentencing for running the biggest hedge fund
insider trading scheme ever has been delayed from Sept. 27 to
Oct. 13.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Bob Van Voris in New York at 
